Description: Fitting (hierarchical) hidden Markov models to financial data
    via maximum likelihood estimation. 
    The package offers different state-dependent distributions (including 
    normal, log-normal, t, Gamma, and Poisson), state decoding, model selection, 
    model checking, and prediction.
    For a reference, see OelschlÃ¤ger, L. and Adam, T. "Detecting bearish and 
    bullish markets in financial time series using  hierarchical hidden Markov 
    models" (2021, Statistical Modelling).
